text: Miyuki Matsuhisa-Hironaka (松久-広中 ミユキ, born August 15, 1945) is a retired Japanese artistic gymnast who competed at the 1968, 1972 and 1976 Summer Olympics. She had her best results in 1968, when her team placed fourth and she shared ninth place on the balance beam. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Japanese female artistic gymnasts
